<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[In a world marked by violence and axiological dissolution, can Word still be good for the individual ethic constitution, as self-knowledge and knowledge of another? This is the question considered by this paper, in which we comment some views of the film Il postino.]]></p></abstract>
